sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API
    participant UserService
    participant UserModel
    participant Database

    User->>API: POST /users/register
    API->>UserService: register_user(data)
    UserService->>UserModel: validate(data)
    UserModel->>Database: INSERT INTO users
    Database-->>UserModel: success
    UserModel-->>UserService: user created
    UserService-->>API: return success
    API-->>User: 201 Created
